Directional OW3D initial-condition batch
Updated: 20-Mar-2026 14:48:47

Purpose
Standalone C++ directional OW3D generation batch using the MF12 spectral implementation.

Workflow
- Full direct spectral reconstruction for each requested phase.
- Surface-only OW3D export.
- Quick-look visualization and field CSV dumps enabled by default.

Current settings snapshot
- output directory = directional initial condition/cpp_large_spreading
- phases = [0, 90, 180, 270] deg
- heading = 0 deg
- spread = 30 deg
- domain = [9008.15, 5630.09] m
- grid = [1025, 257], dx = 8.78844 m, dy = 21.907 m
- surface stride = 8
